            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Now, let's get started!</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced chorizo</strong> and <strong>coriander seeds</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
