          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1931.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>mayonnaise</strong> with <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic paste</strong>, the <strong>dried oregano</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong>, a pinch of<strong> pepper </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>lime juice </strong>– this is your<strong> garlic mayo</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
