      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> avocado<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways, around the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Remove the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> using a teaspoon</p><p>Scoop the<strong> avocado </strong>out of the skin<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>using a spoon, and chop into chunks</p>",
